---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import sartorialMockup from "@/assets/images/sartorial-paris-mockup.webp";
import "@/styles/global.css";
---

<section class="w-full max-w-full overflow-hidden">
	<div class="fixed inset-0 min-w-min h-full -z-10 overflow-hidden">
		<Image
			src={sartorialMockup}
			alt="Sartorial Paris Homepage in a mockup"
			class="w-full h-full object-cover shadow-xl"
			id="MainProjectImage"
			layout="responsive"
			width={4800}
			height={2700}
			sizes="(max-width: 640px) 1280px, (max-width: 768px) 1536px, (max-width: 1024px) 2048px, (max-width: 1920px) 1920px, (max-width: 2560px) 2560px, 4800px"
			quality={100}
			format="webp"
			style="object-fit: cover; object-position: center; height: 100vh;"
			loading="eager"
		/>
		<div
			class="flex-col justify-center content-center fixed bottom-14 left-[50%] -translate-x-[50%] text-sm md:text-base text-white uppercase font-thin tracking-wider"
		>
			<span class="w-full">Scroll</span>
			<span class="flex justify-center items-center w-full"
				><svg
					width="30px"
					height="30px"
					viewBox="0 0 24 24"
					fill="none"
					xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
					><g id="SVGRepo_bgCarrier" stroke-width="0"></g><g
						id="SVGRepo_tracerCarrier"
						stroke-linecap="round"
						stroke-linejoin="round"></g><g id="SVGRepo_iconCarrier">
						<path
							d="M7 10L12 15L17 10"
							stroke="#fff"
							stroke-width="1.5"
							stroke-linecap="round"
							stroke-linejoin="round"></path>
					</g></svg
				></span
			>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="relative top-0 h-screen -z-20"></div>
	<section class="w-full bg-white">
		<section
			class="w-10/12 md:w-3/5 mx-auto md:mt-0 py-14 animate-fade-up animate-duration-700"
			id="about-me"
		>
			<h1 class="text-2xl font-display mt-8 mb-10">
				Sartorial Paris - The Ultimate Menswear Destination
			</h1>
			<ul class="list-none space-y-2 text-base font-textBase">
				<li‚Éó
					>‚Üí <a
						href="https://github.com/ricard0g/sartorial-store"
						class="underline font-textSemiBold text-lg"
						>GitHub Repo</a
					></li‚Éó
				>
				<li>
					‚Üí <a
						href="https://sartorial-store.myshopify.com/"
						class="underline font-textSemiBold text-lg"
						>Sartorial Store Live</a
					> - Password: <i>shorto</i>
				</li>
			</ul>

			<div class="mt-6 mb-12">
				<p class="text-base md:text-lg font-textBase mb-5 text-pretty">
					Sartorial Paris is a fully working online store I built <b
						class="font-textSemiBold">from scratch</b
					> to show what's possible with modern web development.
				</p>

				<blockquote
					class="border-l-4 border-gray-300 pl-4 italic my-8 text-base md:text-lg font-textBase text-gray-700"
				>
					"A place where men can find well-made clothes that combine
					classic Parisian style with modern touches."
				</blockquote>

				<p class="text-base md:text-lg font-textBase mb-5 text-pretty">
					I got my inspiration from <a
						href="https://www.toddsnyder.com/"
						class="underline">Todd Snyder's website</a
					>, but I added my own ideas to make shopping easier and more
					enjoyable.
				</p>
			</div>

			<h2 class="text-xl font-display mt-10 mb-6">
				What I Set Out to Do
			</h2>
			<div class="mb-10">
				<div
					class="bg-gray-50 border-[1px] border-gray-100 p-5 rounded-lg mb-8"
				>
					<p
						class="text-base md:text-lg font-textBase mb-3 text-pretty"
					>
						While Todd Snyder's website was my starting point, I
						wanted to make something that felt fresh and solved
						common shopping frustrations.
					</p>
					<p class="text-base md:text-lg font-textBase text-pretty">
						I focused on <b class="font-textSemiBold"
							>making the site fast and easy to use üéØ</b
						> by carefully choosing the right tools for the job.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<h2 class="text-xl font-display mt-10 mb-6">
				What Makes This Store Special
			</h2>
			<div class="mb-10">
				<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-8">
					<div
						class="border bg-gray-100 border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-5"
					>
						<h3 class="text-lg font-display mb-3">
							üîç Better Navigation
						</h3>
						<ul
							class="list-disc ml-5 space-y-2 text-base font-textBase"
						>
							<li>
								Menu categories that show options when you hover
							</li>
							<li>
								Smart search that predicts what you're looking
								for by implementing the <a
									href="https://shopify.dev/docs/api/ajax/reference/predictive-search"
									class="underline font-textSemiBold"
									>Predictive Search API</a
								> from scratch
							</li>
							<li>Navbar that follows you as you scroll</li>
							<li>Mobile menu that's actually easy to use</li>
						</ul>
					</div>

					<div
						class="border bg-gray-100 border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-5"
					>
						<h3 class="text-lg font-display mb-3">
							üéØ Smooth Product Browsing
						</h3>
						<ul
							class="list-disc ml-5 space-y-2 text-base font-textBase"
						>
							<li>Touch-friendly product sliders</li>
							<li>
								Quick-view product details without page loads
							</li>
							<li>Continuous shopping without interruptions</li>
						</ul>
					</div>

					<div
						class="bg-gray-100 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-5"
					>
						<h3 class="text-lg font-display mb-3">
							üîé Finding What You Want
						</h3>
						<ul
							class="list-disc ml-5 space-y-2 text-base font-textBase"
						>
							<li>
								Filters that understand what you're looking for
								through a full custom implementation of <a
									class="underline font-textSemiBold"
									href="https://shopify.dev/docs/storefronts/themes/navigation-search/filtering/storefront-filtering"
									>Shopify's Storefront Filtering</a
								> where the <a
									class="underline font-textSemiBold"
									href="https://shopify.dev/docs/storefronts/themes/navigation-search/filtering/storefront-filtering/storefront-filtering-ux"
									>UX guidelines</a
								> were the highest priority
							</li>
							<li>
								Smart sorting by size, color, and other features
							</li>
							<li>
								Tag-based filtering that works on any device
							</li>
						</ul>
					</div>

					<div
						class="border bg-gray-100 border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-5"
					>
						<h3 class="text-lg font-display mb-3">
							üëî Helpful Suggestions
						</h3>
						<ul
							class="list-disc ml-5 space-y-2 text-base font-textBase"
						>
							<li>
								"You might also like" based on what you're
								viewing throught the <a
									class="underline font-textSemiBold"
									href="https://shopify.dev/docs/api/ajax/reference/product-recommendations"
									>Product Recommendations API</a
								>
							</li>
							<li>
								Fresh content that updates as you browse thanks
								to <a
									class="underline font-textSemiBold"
									href="https://shopify.dev/docs/api/ajax/section-rendering"
									>Section Rendering API</a
								>
							</li>
							<li>Personalized product discovery</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div
					class="border bg-gray-100 border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-5 mb-8"
				>
					<h3 class="text-lg font-display mb-3">
						üõí Smart Shopping Cart
					</h3>
					<p class="text-base font-textBase mb-3">
						I built a cart that <b class="font-textSemiBold"
							>just works</b
						> the way you'd expect, implementing the <a
							class="underline font-textSemiBold"
							href="https://shopify.dev/docs/api/ajax/reference/cart"
							>Cart API</a
						>:
					</p>
					<ul
						class="list-disc ml-5 space-y-2 text-base font-textBase"
					>
						<li>Built from scratch to be fast and reliable</li>
						<li>Price and quantity updates happen instantly</li>
						<li>Checkout process that's straightforward</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</div>

			<h2 class="text-xl font-display mt-10 mb-6">How I Built It</h2>
			<div class="mb-10">
				<div
					class="bg-gray-50 border-[1px] border-gray-100 p-5 rounded-lg mb-6"
				>
					<h3 class="text-lg font-display mb-3">
						üöÄ Simple Tools, Great Results
					</h3>
					<div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-4">
						<span class="bg-gray-200 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm"
							>HTML</span
						>
						<span class="bg-gray-200 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm"
							>CSS</span
						>
						<span class="bg-gray-200 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm"
							>Liquid</span
						>
						<span class="bg-gray-200 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm"
							>JavaScript</span
						>
						<span class="bg-gray-200 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm"
							>jQuery</span
						>
					</div>
					<p class="text-base md:text-lg font-textBase text-pretty">
						I used basic web technologies to build something
						powerful. You don't always need fancy frameworks to make
						something that works well.
					</p>
				</div>

				<div class="border bg-gray-100 border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-5">
					<h3 class="text-lg font-display mb-3">
						üì≤ Keeping It Simple
					</h3>
					<p
						class="text-base md:text-lg font-textBase mb-3 text-pretty"
					>
						Instead of relying on tons of apps and plugins, I wrote
						custom code to get exactly what I wanted.
					</p>
					<div class="bg-gray-100 p-3 rounded-lg">
						<p class="text-base font-textSemiBold">
							Only One App Used:
						</p>
						<p class="text-base font-textBase">
							Just a search and filtering app - everything else is
							custom-built
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<h2 class="text-xl font-display mt-10 mb-6">What I'm Proud Of</h2>
			<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 mb-10">
				<div
					class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg flex flex-col items-center text-center"
				>
					<div class="text-3xl mb-2">üí´</div>
					<h3 class="text-lg font-display mb-2">
						User-Friendly Design
					</h3>
					<p class="text-sm font-textBase">
						Small touches that make shopping more enjoyable
					</p>
				</div>

				<div
					class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg flex flex-col items-center text-center"
				>
					<div class="text-3xl mb-2">üèÜ</div>
					<h3 class="text-lg font-display mb-2">Clean Code</h3>
					<p class="text-sm font-textBase">
						Built right so it's fast and doesn't break
					</p>
				</div>

				<div
					class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg flex flex-col items-center text-center"
				>
					<div class="text-3xl mb-2">üîÑ</div>
					<h3 class="text-lg font-display mb-2">
						Everything Works Together
					</h3>
					<p class="text-sm font-textBase">
						A smooth experience from browsing to checkout
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="border-t border-gray-200 pt-8 mt-8">
				<p class="text-base md:text-lg font-textBase text-pretty">
					This project shows that with careful planning and attention
					to detail, you can build an online store that looks great,
					works well, and keeps customers coming back.
				</p>
			</div>
		</section>
	</section>
</section>
